<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Baloo+2:wght@600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/base.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/login.css">
    <title>LatMia</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="side-bar">
        <div class="logo-background"> <img src="assets/images/logo_dog_and_cat.webp" alt="logo" class="logo-img"></div>
        <p class="side-tagline">Cada patinha merece<br>um lar para chamar de seu</p>
    </div>
    <main>
        <div class="content-wrap">
            <span class="eyebrow">🐾 Bem-vindo de volta</span>
            <p class="intro-text">Lar de adoção para cães e gatos</p>
            <p class="intro-subtext">Entre na sua conta para acompanhar adoções, atualizar perfis de pets e encontrar o
                match perfeito para cada família.</p>

            <form action="#" method="get">
                <div class="form-container">

                    <span class="form-title">Entre em sua conta</span>

                    <div class="input-container">
                        <label for="user-email">EMAIL</label>
                        <input type="email" name="user-email" id="user-email" placeholder="voce@exemplo.com" required>
                    </div>

                    <div class="input-container">
                        <label for="user-password">SENHA</label>
                        <input type="password" name="user-password" id="user-password" placeholder="••••••••" required>
                    </div>

                </div>
                <div class="button-container">
                    <button type="submit" class="submit-button">Entrar</button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>

        <p class="footer-note">© 2026 LatMia · Adoção responsável de cães e gatos</p>
    </main>
</body>
<script src="/form.login.js"></script>

</html>